{"tid":749830,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[憤青]乜都睇唔順眼，週街鬧人 ，係咪要睇精神科？","createTime":"2018-07-20T10:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T21:19:40.000Z","uid":615,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82829d12a4971c4fbda7428f664332e3ad6dbd21","tid":749830,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"每日返工放工、覺得條街好迫好多人，行行下抖唔到氣<br />\n俾人掂到少少就想開波屌鳩條友<br />\n返到公司樓上裝修鑽牆、隔離band房日日打鼓開party，已經嘈到分唔清係乜聲，時時刻刻有幻聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工仲未計未客屌、俾老細監視，真係好大壓力，好辛苦，我係咪應該要睇下醫生？<br />\n<br />\n連動力、興趣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec810a2c483ec45e25e288fb0c0f9394d3fe57b","tid":749830,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1irclq8QG2YyQTec2p/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1irclq8QG2YyQTec2p%2Fgiphy.gif&h=109dfea5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b796c5505e1d905e31fd54cb7b6e472678f325","tid":749830,"uid":186163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得d野好煩，我就黎爆炸"},{"pid":"528e5d98fb54942ce42ea27972754a03cc6d7a75","tid":749830,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b796c5505e1d905e31fd54cb7b6e472678f325","tid":749830,"uid":186163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得d野好煩，我就黎爆炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"醒啦"},{"pid":"8162fd8980e78f8f5830f27aca21a54887ad20ab","tid":749830,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ba200c389c4a306a0e37be308c805546811158","tid":749830,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T20:43:14.000Z"